               stealing, on the <rs id="t18280911-393-cd2043" type="crimeDate">9th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-393-off2042 t18280911-393-cd2043"></join>, 3lbs. weight of cheese, value 1s. 6d.; 4lbs. weight of ham, value 2s.; 1 tub, value 6d.; and 4 cloths, value 1s.; the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18280911-393-victim2107" type="victimName">
                        John Green 
                        Winter
                     <interp inst="t18280911-393-victim2107" type="surname" value="Winter"></interp>
